    S:gt.blockmachines.amazonprime.controller.tier.single.tooltip_secondary.15513=§fDimensions: §65§7x§63§7x§63§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front right, 2nd layer\n§6   4x §r§7Supply Depot Casings (minimum)\n§6   3x §r§7Item Pipe (tiered)\n§6   2x §r§7Iron Frame Box\n§6   3x §r§7Any Tiered Glass (tiered)\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any casing\n§f   Muffler Hatch: §7Any casing\n   Uses sub channel §6glass§r§7 for §6Glass Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6item_pipe§r§7 for §6Item Pipe Casing Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
