    S:gt.blockmachines.basicmachine.industrialapiary.tooltip=BEES GOES BRRRR\n§7Author: §a§4§lk§c§lu§6§lb§e§la§2§l6§a§l0§b§l0§3§l0§r§7\nEffective production chance as a percent is\n2.8 * b^0.52 * (p + t)^0.52 * s^0.37\nwhere b is the base production chance as a percent,\np is the production modifier (2 w/o upgrades, or 4 * 1.2^n with n production upgrades),\nt is 8 for the industrial apiary, and\ns is the speed value for the bee\nOutputs are generated at the end of every bee tick (...)\nPrimary outputs are rolled once with base chance, once with half base
