    S:gt.blockmachines.componentassemblyline.tooltip=Machine Type: §eHigh-Capacity Component Assembler, CoAL§r\nAssembles basic components (motors, pumps, etc.) in large batches\nThe §l§eComponent Assembly Line Casing §r§7limits the recipes the machine can perform. See the NEI pages for details\nUsing casings above the required recipe tier provides a speed bonus:\n§eHalves recipe time per tier above recipe\n§oMuch more efficient than other competing brands!\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\nThis machine can run recipes regardless of tier, if given enough energy\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nAdded by: §a§bMadMan310§r§7
