    S:gt.blockmachines.dehp.tooltip=Machine Type: §eGeothermal Heat Pump, DEHP§r\nConsumes 480EU/t\nHas 2 Modes, use the Screwdriver to change them:\nDirect Steam and Coolant Heating\nDirect Steam Mode: Consumes §9Distilled Water§7 to produce §f512000§7L/s of §fSuperheated Steam\nCoolant Heating Mode: Converts 3840L/s §bCoolant§7 to §cHot Coolant\nEach maintenance issue lowers output efficiency by §a10%\nExplodes when it runs out of Distilled Water/Coolant\nBase cycle time: 1 tick\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nAdded by: §a§abartimaeusnek§7 via §2BartWorks§r§7
