    S:gt.blockmachines.gtpp.multimachine.rocketengine.name=Rocketdyne F-1A 엔진
    S:gt.blockmachines.gtpp.multimachine.rocketengine.tooltip=Machine Type: §eRocket Engine§r\nGenerating Power from Rocket Fuels\nSupply GT++ Rocket Fuels and 1000L of Carbon Dioxide per hour\nProduces as much energy as you put fuel in, with optional boosting\nThis multi doesn't accept fluids if not enabled - enable it first!\nConsumes 2000L/s of air and pollutes 1500 gibbl/s per 16384 eu/t produced\nPlace 1-8 Air Intake Hatches on the sides to maintain Air input\nIf it runs out of air, it will shut down and have to be manually restarted\nSupply 3L of Liquid Hydrogen per second, per 1000 EU/t to boost\nTakes 3x the amount of Carbon Dioxide and maintains efficiency\nFuel efficiency starts at ~160%, falls more slowly at higher EU/t if boosted\nIf producing more than 30k EU/t, fuel efficiency will be lower:\n(These thresholds are 3x higher when boosted, boosted values displayed second)\n- 75% of max fuel efficiency at 53k or 159k EU/t output energy\n- 50% of max fuel efficiency at 69k or 207k EU/t output energy\n- 25% of max fuel efficiency at 98k or 294k EU/t output energy\nformula: x = input of energy (30000^(1/3)/ x^(1/3)) * (80000^(1/3)/ x^(1/3))\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
