    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.airfilter.01.name=전기식 공기 필터 T1
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.airfilter.01.tooltip=Machine Type: §eAir Filter, EAF§r\nNeeds a Turbine in the controller\nCan process 3x3 chunks\nEach muffler hatch reduces pollution in one chunk of the working area by:\n  §f30.0 * multiTierBonus * turbineEff * FLOOR(2.5^mufflerTier)\nevery second\n- multiTierBonus for this controller is 1.0\n- turbineEff is the efficiency of the Turbine in controller slot\n- Effective muffler tier is limited by energy input tier\n- Uses 30 EU/t while working\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nInsert Absorption Filter in an input bus\n  to double pollution cleaning amount (30 uses per item)\nEach maintenance issue reduces cleaning amount by 10%\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.airfilter.01.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §63§7x§64§7x§63§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§f   Air Filter Turbine Casing: §7Top and bottom layers\n§f   Air Filter Vent Casing: §7Corners of the middle two layers\n§f   Muffler Hatch: §7Sides of the middle two layers\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any bottom layer casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any bottom layer casing\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any bottom layer casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any bottom layer casing\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
