    S:gt.blockmachines.orewashingplant.controller.tier.single.tooltip=Machine Type: §eOre Washer, Simple Washer§r\n§64§7 Parallels per §fVoltage§7 Tier\n§a500%§7 Speed\n§8100%§7 EU Usage\nCan be configured with a screwdriver to also be used as Simple Washer\nAlways requires an Input Hatch full of water to refill structure\nNeed to be filled with water\nWill automatically fill water from Input Hatch\n§5100 §7Pollution per second\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nStructure by: §a§6ya9yu§r§7
    S:gt.blockmachines.orewashingplant.controller.tier.single.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §65§7x§64§7x§69§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center\n§6   70x §r§7Wash Plant Casing (minimum)\n§6   7x §r§7Steel Gear Box Casing\n§6   15x §r§7Steel Frame Box\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Wash Plant Casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Wash Plant Casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any Wash Plant Casing\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any Wash Plant Casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Wash Plant Casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Wash Plant Casing\n§f   Muffler Hatch: §7Any Wash Plant Casing\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.pipe.bec.block.tooltip=§7Connects several Bose-Einstein Condensate multiblocks together into a network.\n§7Multiblocks must have a §6Bose-Einstein Condensate Hatch§6§7 that connects to a conduit to connect to the network.\n§7Use a §6Bose-Einstein Condensate Maxwell Gate§6§7 to control the flow of condensate.\n§7Can split and turn - multiblocks just have to be connected to link together.\n§7Will only connect to pipes and hatches that match its color.\n§3§lExplosion proof
