    S:gt.blockmachines.preciseassembler.name=정밀 자동 조립기 MT-3662
    S:gt.blockmachines.preciseassembler.tooltip=Machine Type: §ePrecise Assembler, Assembler, PrAss§r\nNo more than 7nm of error\nHas Two Modes: Precise and Normal\nUse a Screwdriver to change modes\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nPrecise Mode unlocks the ability to assemble precise components\nCasing Tier determines Maximum Recipe Tier\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nNormal Mode allows standard assembler recipes\n§fPrecise Casing§7 Tier determines §6Parallels§7\n§aImprecise§7/§9Mk-I§7/§dMK-II§7/§6MK-III§7/§cMK-IV§7->§a16§7/§932§7/§d64§7/§6128§7/§c256§7 Parallels\n§a200%§7 Speed\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nMachine Casing limits the voltage tier the machine can work on, §4§nUHV§7-tier Machine Casing unlocks all.\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\nThis machine can only run recipes matching its average energy hatch tier\n§5780 §7Pollution per second\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.preciseassembler.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §69§7x§65§7x§65§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§6   21x §r§7Machine Casing (tiered)\n§6   42x §r§7Any Tiered Glass (EV+)\n§6   42x§7 - §686x §r§7Precise Electronic Unit Casing (tiered)\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any Casing\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Casing\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any Casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Casing\n§f   Muffler Hatch: §7Any Casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Casing\n   Uses sub channel §6glass§r§7 for §6Glass Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6unit_casing§r§7 for §6Precise Electronic Unit Casing Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6machine_casing§r§7 for §6Machine Casing Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
